metadata.name: Fearless
metadata.description: Fearless represents fashion, which faces the unknown and has fascination for the unusual. Sci-fi elements are part of this collection and make it look weirdly beautiful. Fascination for the possibility of the existence of life outside the Earth have always been topics, whether in the entertainment industry or in the fashion industry. Armor elements in the mini dress are combined with two-tone organic looking flower elements. Fearless is a glimpse into the future, a mix of nature and technology. A glimpse into distant planets and abstract architecture.
